{"id":326808,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/12/global-voices-用16种语言说明加泰隆尼亚独立/","date":"2013-12-22T16:15:23Z","modified":"2013-12-22T16:15:23Z","title":"Global Voices | 用16种语言说明“加泰隆尼亚独立”","content":"<p><p>“加泰隆尼亚计划（<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://thecatalanproject.org/en\">The Catalan Project</a>）”(<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/Catalan_Project\">@Catalan_Project</a>)的首支<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?annotation_id=annotation_1047819143&#038;feature=iv&#038;src_vid=p96OvGSneec&#038;v=xY_Lnf24-xM#t=2s\">影片</a>，由自称“来自加利西亚的加泰隆尼亚人与西班牙人”Fernando de Castro领衔，透过他会说的16种语言，介绍这个计划，并说明为什么<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/12/17/catalonia-independence-from-spain-to-do-what/\">有些加泰隆尼亚人想要自西班牙独立</a>。可以选择的字幕有<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?annotation_id=annotation_1047819143&#038;feature=iv&#038;src_vid=p96OvGSneec&#038;v=xY_Lnf24-xM#t=2s\">英文</a>、<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1L07QetzMGY\">法文</a>、<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WbqLKZhO3A0\">德文</a>、<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N4vsiExWdxA&#038;feature=youtu.be\">西班牙文</a>与<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p96OvGSneec&#038;feature=youtu.be\">加泰隆尼亚文</a>。</p>\n<p>“<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://thecatalanproject.org/en\">加泰隆尼亚计划</a>”是个独立且非营利的组织。这个计划提供开放的线上平台，让“所有在加泰隆尼亚工作或生活、对于如何创建一个更好的国家有想法的公民”，能够来讨论未来独立的加泰隆尼亚应该是什么样子。因为，“独立不是终点，而是起点。”这个计划目前在群众集资网站<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.verkami.com/projects/6314-the-catalan-project\">Verkami</a>上有募资活动。</p>\n<div>校对：Fen</div>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/violeta_camarasa/\" title=\"文章导读 Violeta Camarasa\">Violeta Camarasa</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/ameli/\" title=\"文章导读 Ameli\">Ameli</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/11/20/catalan-independence-debate-explained-in-16-languages/\" title=\"阅读原文  en\">阅读原文  en</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2013/12/23/13042/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br /><span><span>分享: </span> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E7%94%A816%E7%A7%8D%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E2%80%9C%E5%8A%A0%E6%B3%B0%E9%9A%86%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9A%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E2%80%9D&#038;url=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F12%2F23%2F13042%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F12%2F23%2F13042%2F&#038;desc=%E7%94%A816%E7%A7%8D%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E2%80%9C%E5%8A%A0%E6%B3%B0%E9%9A%86%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9A%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E2%80%9D\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F12%2F23%2F13042%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F12%2F23%2F13042%2F&#038;text=%E7%94%A816%E7%A7%8D%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E2%80%9C%E5%8A%A0%E6%B3%B0%E9%9A%86%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9A%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E2%80%9D&#038;via=